<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>키티서버</title>
<meta name="description" content="키티서버 공식 사이트">

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Apple SD Gothic Neo,Noto Sans KR,sans-serif;
  background:#0b0f1a;
  color:#e9eefc;
}

.wrap{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px}
.card{
  background:#121a2b;
  border:1px solid #22304f;
  border-radius:18px;
  padding:22px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25)
}

/* ===== 배너 ===== */
.banner-wrap{
  position:relative;
  overflow:hidden;
  border-radius:14px;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.banner-img{
  width:100%;
  display:block;
}

.shine{
  position:absolute;
  top:0;
  left:-40%;
  width:40%;
  height:100%;
  background:linear-gradient(
    120deg,
    rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0.35) 50%,
    rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%
  );
  transform:skewX(-20deg);
  animation:shineMove 3.5s infinite;
}

@keyframes shineMove{
  0%{ left:-40% }
  100%{ left:140% }
}
/* ===== 끝 ===== */

.top{display:flex;gap:18px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.logo{
  width:76px;height:76px;border-radius:18px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff4fd8,#6aa8ff);
  display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800
}

h1{margin:0;font-size:28px}
.sub{margin:6px 0 0;color:#b9c6e6}

.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px;margin-top:16px}
@media(min-width:820px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}

.box{
  background:#0f1626;
  border:1px solid #22304f;
  border-radius:14px;
  padding:16px
}

.box h2{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:16px}
.btns{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:14px}

a.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:10px 14px;
  border-radius:12px;
  text-decoration:none;
  color:#0b0f1a;
  background:#e9eefc;
  font-weight:700
}

a.btn.secondary{
  background:transparent;
  color:#e9eefc;
  border:1px solid #3a4f7a
}

.footer{margin-top:18px;color:#93a4c7;font-size:12px}
.tag{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:4px 10px;
  border-radius:999px;
  background:#192643;
  border:1px solid #2a3a61;
  color:#cfe0ff;
  font-size:12px;
  margin-right:6px
}
.list{margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#cfe0ff}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="wrap">
<div class="card">

<!-- ===== 애니메이션 배너 ===== -->
<div class="banner-wrap">
  <img src="banner_glow_open_fix.jpg" class="banner-img">
  <div class="shine"></div>
</div>
<!-- ===================== -->

<div class="top">
  <div class="logo">KITTY</div>
  <div>
    <h1>키티서버</h1>
    <div class="sub">공식 사이트 · 다운로드 · 커뮤니티</div>
    <div style="margin-top:10px">
      <span class="tag">비영리</span>
      <span class="tag">2차 오픈</span>
      <span class="tag">커뮤니티</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid">

<div class="box">
<h2>📢 공지</h2>
<ul class="list">
<li>3월 1일 ~ 8일 2차 오픈</li>
<li>디스코드 및 단톡 참여 후 접속</li>
<li>오대기: 3월 1일 17시</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h2>⬇️ 다운로드</h2>
<div class="btns">
<a class="btn secondary" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1T-wStrkUTliUxCikulXoJo4ZmJS9AVVp/view" target="_blank">접속기 다운로드</a>
</div>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h2>💬 커뮤니티</h2>
<div class="btns">
<a class="btn secondary" href="https://discord.gg/ecBhq6Y9" target="_blank">Discord</a>
<a class="btn secondary" href="https://open.kakao.com/o/g7MGDzdi" target="_blank">카카오 단톡</a>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">© 키티서버</div>

</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
